content.p: The School of Biosciences at the Malaysia Campus offers a series of exciting first degree and higher degree programmes in the areas of Nutrition, Biotechnology and Plant Biotechnology. All degrees awarded at the Malaysia campus are the same as those conferred in the UK. Please follow the links below to learn more about course structure, content and entry requirements. telephone: +6 (03) 8924 8000 fax: +6 (03) 8924 8018
